Procedure to share the CSV document with Vendor

Import Data without a Format File, using BCP utility 



bcp <db_name>.<schema>.<table_name IN D:\BCP\<file>.bcp -T -c
Import Data with a Non-XML Format File 



bcp <db_name>.<schema>.<table_name> IN D:\BCP\file.bcp -f D:\BCP\file.fmt -T
Import data using BULK INSERT and Character Format without a Format File 



USE <Db_name>
go
BULK INSERT <db_name>.<schema>.<table_name>  
   FROM 'abc.txt'
WITH (
        DATAFILETYPE = 'Char'
        ); 
GO
Using BULK INSERT and Character Format with a Non-XML Format File 



USE <Db_name>
go
BULK INSERT <db_name>.<schema>.<table_name>  
   FROM 'abc.txt'
WITH (
        FORMATFILE = 'D:\BCP\file.fmt'
        ); 
GO
Using OPEN ROWSET and Character Format with a Non-XML Format File 



INSERT INTO <db_name>.<schema>.<table_name>
    SELECT *
    FROM OPENROWSET (
        BULK 'D:\BCP\file.bcp', 
        FORMATFILE = 'D:\BCP\file.fmt'  
        ) AS t1;
Export Data Using BCP Utility 

Open the CMD prompt and enter the query below



bcp <db_name>.<Schema>.<table> OUT D:\BCP\<name>.bcp -T -c
to Review Result 



NOTEPAD D:\BCP\<name>.bcp
